http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Armed-bikers-rob-milk-vendor/article14023139.ece

Armed duo on a motorcycle attacked and robbed a milk vendor at Ramamurthynagar early on Wednesday.The victim, Vinod Kumar, is a resident of B. Narayanapura. He was driving his goods van carrying milk packets for distribution when two men on a motorcycle intercepted his vehicle and demanded money at knife point.Vinod Kumar handed over the cash he was carrying. The duo also took his mobile phone. Enraged that Vinod Kumar did not have more than Rs. 500 on him, the duo attacked him with the knife before speeding away.The Ramamurthynagar police, who have registered a case of robbery, said Vinod Kumar sustained multiple injuries but managed to reach CMH Hospital.